14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2802.1A of Title 68, unless
17 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 A. For the 2026 assessment year and each assessment year
19 thereafter, with respect to any commercial buildings constructed
20 without final interior elements such as finished ceilings, finished
21 floors, interior walls, lighting fixtures, cabinetry work, and
22 similar features, if the owner of the real property upon which the
23 commercial buildings are constructed or the contractor responsible
24 for the construction of the commercial building intends to either
